**Presenter: Jae-Hoon (John) Jeong**
**Slides:** [Use Cases and Practices for Intent-Based Networking](https://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/125/materials/slides-125-nmrg-use-cases-and-practices-for-intent-based-networking-00)
